b'{"data_headers":{"result_code":1},"data":{"information":{"article_id":161,"category_name":"News","pr_category_id":"1","title_name":"About Changes to the Amount of Rupies Obtainable from Rupie Mines","message":"<div>As part of the adjustments to rupies, mana, and crystals described in What&#39;s Ahead for Dragalia Lost, Part 1, we will increase the amount of rupies that can be obtained from rupie mines in the Halidom.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>These changes to the rupie mines will be applied at <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1545890400\\"><\/span>.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0 Changes:<\/div><div>The amount of rupies obtained, and the time it takes to obtain them, will be adjusted according to the facility level as described below.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u30fb Lv. 1<\/div><div>Before: Production Time - 6 hours, Rupie Capacity - 800<\/div><div>After: Production Time - 8 hours, Rupie Capacity - 2,640<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u30fb Lv. 10<\/div><div>Before: Production Time - 6 hours, Rupie Capacity - 1,250<\/div><div>After: Production Time - 8 hours, Rupie Capacity - 4,130<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u30fb Lv. 20<\/div><div>Before: Production Time - 6 hours, Rupie Capacity - 1,750<\/div><div>After: Production Time - 8 hours, Rupie Capacity - 5,780<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Rupies are used for crafting weapons and building facilities in your Halidom, so build rupie mines and put them to good use!<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0 Note:<\/div><div>\\u30fb Because we&#39;re making this change, your rupie mines will reach capacity at <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1545890400\\"><\/span>. At that time, you may not see any visible difference in your rupie mines or receive a notification that your rupie mine reached capacity at <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1545890400\\"><\/span>.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Thank you for playing the Dragalia Lost game.<\/div>","start_time":1545302700,"prev_article_id":"163","next_article_id":"162","image_path":"","update_time":1545302237}}}'